text: March 9, 2018 / 7:40 PM / Updated 28 minutes ago BRIEF-Nova Leap Health Continues To See Co Exiting 2018 With A $10 Mln Rev Run Rate Reuters Staff March 9 (Reuters) - Nova Leap Health Corp: * NOVA LEAP HEALTH CORP. REPORTS FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL YEAR 2017 FINANCIAL RESULTS * NOVA LEAP HEALTH CORP - MANAGEMENT CONTINUES TO EXPECT THAT COMPANY WILL EXIT 2018 WITH A $10 MILLION REVENUE RUN RATE * NOVA LEAP HEALTH CORP - CONTINUES TO EXPLORE AND EVALUATE OPPORTUNITIES FOR ACQUISITION OF HOME CARE BUSINESSES Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
